text:
130-144 Bushwick Ave., west side, north from Ten Eyck Street. At left foreground, is No. 144 Bushwick Ave.

October 25, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

*ASSUMING STREET TO BE NORTH AND SOUTH*

text:
Bushwick Ave., east side, between Ten Eyck and Stagg Streets, showing Public School No. 36, at left background; at the right, is seen part of St. Catherine's Hospital.

September 27, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.

ASSUMING STREET TO BE NORTH AND SOUTH
